00Z","msg":"畀左幾多百億畀國泰？"},{"pid":"74d9b46c62e6f25288694c86410449389427ffde","tid":2510742,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"加税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開銷售税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陸路離境税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燃油税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車牌牌費加一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣樓加一倍税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n股票印花稅再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f0013c0517990983efef3a232025eced990248","tid":2510742,"uid":13545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"說好的有國安法就經濟繁榮呢？"},{"pid":"33c0a30c33e7b3e1211196ddb723542c0e55013f","tid":2510742,"uid":64165,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7797276c0cbf0d097963a0334936040a047369fe","tid":2510742,"uid":24788,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<br />\n前幾日重建警察宿舍要20億<br />\n警察財政預算258億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但全港薪俸稅收入得600幾億"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"香港人交稅一半養狗<br />\n另一半養蝗"}]}